events.description:
The Southern Polytechnic State University coaching
staff wishes to teach, motivate and help all players (girls and boys) reach her/his potential. This is a basketball camp where we strive to teach every aspect of the game while at the same time teaching campers how to be winners in the 'game' of life. A typical day features two games, a daily contest, ball-handling, post moves, fundamental of the day, and chalk talk with Coach Dawkins. Free t-shirt, work-out program, and more!
